    • Constructor Detail

      • ProductDetailsBuilder

        public ProductDetailsBuilder(android.content.Context context)
        Create a default ProductDetailsBuilder. If this constructor is used, setShopDomain(String), setApplicationName(String), setApiKey(String), setChannelid(String), and setProductId(String) must be called.
        Parameters:
        context - context to use for starting the Activity

      • ProductDetailsBuilder

        public ProductDetailsBuilder(android.content.Context context,
                             BuyClient client)
        Constructor that will use an existing BuyClient to configure the ProductDetailsActivity. If this constructor is user, setProductId(String) must be called.
        Parameters:
        context - context to use for launching the Activity
        client - the BuyClient to use to configure the ProductDetailsActivity
